First Name: #1.First Name,Last Name,Email id and Company Name are mandatory Fields. If any of the mandatory field is blank, then user will not be created.
#2.Leave blank for 2FA, if you do not want to enable 2FA.
#3.If 2FA is enabled at dataroom level and if you leave blank for 2FA, by default Email Mode will be selected.
#4.If 2FA mode is selected as Mobile or Whatsapp, Phone Country Code and Phone number are mandatory. If Phone Country Code and/or Phone number are blank, then by default Email Mode will be selected.
